  "title": "(ENTRY-LEVEL) SALES AND MARKETING AMBASSADOR",
  "description": "<p>Want a job that pushes you, pays you well, and builds real confidence?</p><p>At <strong>Thrive Organisation</strong>, every day is a challenge — and every win is yours.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br />• Talk to people & represent brands<br />• Learn sales skills that actually matter<br />• Work in a fast, high-energy environment<br />• Be part of a team that pushes you to level up</p><p><strong>What You’ll Get:</strong><br />• 📈 Fast progression — clear steps to grow<br />• 💪 Real confidence & people skills<br />• 🤝 A solid team that has your back<br />• ⚡ No boring desk work</p><p><strong>We want individuals who:</strong><br />• Are competitive in a good way<br />• Like challenges & fast-paced work<br />• Want personal growth, not just a paycheck<br />• Bring drive, discipline & good energy</p><p>If you want a role that rewards effort and builds you up —<br /><strong>Apply now and rise with us.</strong> 🚀🔥</p>",
